Collection. In the 12 months prior to the effective date of this Privacy Notice, we collected, and will continue to collect, the following categories of Personal Information from California residents:

Personal Identifiers: such as name, address, telephone number, email address, age, birthday and month, username and password for our websites, online identifiers, IP address;
Demographic Information: such as gender;
Commercial Information: such as products purchased or considered for purchase, purchase histories or tendencies, and loyalty program participation information;
Payment Information: such as Credit or Debit Card number; Credit or Debit Card expiration date; Credit or Debit Card security code;
Site or App Usage Information: such as internet connection information, pages visited, advertising data, and site logging information;
Geolocation Information: including precise location data and physical location information when you visit our site or use our apps on your mobile device;
Audio and Visual Information: such as in-store security video and customer service audio recordings; and
Inferences Drawn from Above Categories: such as your preferences, characteristics, and purchasing behaviors.

Sharing for Business Purposes. We may share the categories of Personal Information listed below with third party service providers, who may use your information only for purposes of providing services to Papa Johns.

In the 12 months prior to the effective date of this Privacy Notice, we shared, and will continue to share, the following categories of information with service providers:

Personal Identifiers: such as name, address, telephone number, email address, age, date of birth, username and password for our websites, online identifiers, IP address;
Demographic Information: such as gender;
Commercial Information: such as products purchased or considered for purchase, purchase histories or tendencies, and loyalty program participation information;
Site or App Usage Information: such as internet connection information, pages visited, advertising data, and site logging information;
Geolocation Information: including precise location data and physical location information when you visit our site or use our apps on your mobile device;
Audio and Visual Information: such as in-store security video and customer service audio recordings; and
Inferences Drawn from Above Categories: such as your preferences, characteristics, and purchasing behaviors.

Right to Know
California residents have the right to request certain types of information regarding the Personal Information we have collected about you in the 12 months prior to your request (subject to exceptions):

Specific pieces of Personal Information;
Categories of Personal Information;
Categories of sources from which we collected your Personal Information;
Categories of your Personal Information that we sold to or shared with third parties, or disclosed to service providers for a business purpose; and
The business purposes for collecting or selling your Personal Information.
